description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 61, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 122, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and 8 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50612-12182-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [122 Votes, Top 15% Score]
